.SH Name
.SP 5 5
rip - rip the heart from a fallen enemy and eat it!
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
rip <corpse>
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
After you have slain an enemy, this useful command will allow you to rip out the beast's heart and feast upon it. This gruesome act will not only look disgusting to outsiders, but it will also heal you a few hitpoints!


.El

